          </content>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
          <num>•</num>
          <content>
            <p>The Queen’s Speech 2022: Background briefing notes: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/queens-speech-2022-background-briefing-notes"><u>https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/queens-speech-2022-background-briefing-notes</u></a></p>
          </content>
        </paragraph>
